        <h2 data-children-count=3D"0">Salon/Spa:</h2>
<table style=3D"width:100%; border: 1px solid black;">
        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <th>Service</th>
                <th>Tip</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Hair Salon</td>
                <td>15-20%, ask to be split among those who served you</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Manicurist</td>
                <td>15-20%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Facial, Waxing, Massage</td>
                <td>15-20%</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
<p></p>
<p>For more information, read about the <a title=3D"The Finer Points of Tip=
ping" href=3D"https://emilypost.com/advice/finer-points-of-tipping" target=
=3D"_blank">finer points of tipping</a>, <a href=3D"https://emilypost.com/a=
dvice/end-of-summer-tipping-guide">end of summer tipping guide</a>,&nbsp;an=
d <a title=3D"Holiday Tipping" href=3D"https://emilypost.com/advice/holiday=
-tipping-guide" target=3D"_blank">holiday tipping</a>.</p>
    </div>
</section>
